item.title: Sample
item.description: no tracking what does that mean? I had to remind myself why I’m writing this blog at all: First and foremost, I write for myself. For the pleasure of writing, to keep notes and to structure thoughts. If any of this turns out to be useful for others, great, glad I could help. No need to spy on my visitors. Benefits data privacy performance peace of mind no comments really? Let’s face it: Static site generators are simply not made for this.
